ca.uqac.lif.ecp

Class CayleyDiameterCoverage<T extends Event,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.CoverageMetric<T,V>
      • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.CayleyCoverageMetric<T,U,Float>
        • ca.uqac.lif.ecp.CayleyDiameterCoverage<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of events in the trace
    U - The output type of the triaging function

    public class CayleyDiameterCoverage<T extends Event,U>
extends CayleyCoverageMetric<T,U,Float>
    Coverage of a set of traces based on the maximum length for which all equivalence classes of some triaging function are represented in one of the prefixes of some trace. Otherwise stated, it is the largest integer d such that the subgraph of the Cayley graph with diameter d is completely covered by the traces of the set.
    Author:
    Sylvain
